data.description: BETTER BE QUICK TO THIS GORGEOUS TOWNHOME IN THE HEART OF PALM HARBOR. THIS 2 BED 2.5 BATH TOWNHOME HAS A LARGE LIVING AREA, WIDE OPEN LAYOUT, KITCHEN OVERLOOKS THE LIVING ROOM ,NEW A/C , NEWER APPLIANCES, SCREENED PORCHES OFF THE KITCHEN AND MASTER BEDROOM.  MASTER FEATURES AN ENSUITE,  LOTS OF CLOSET SPACE, LOTS OF STORAGE SPACE. HOME FEATURES 2 RESERVED PARKING SPOTS DIRECTLY IN FRONT OF THE UNIT..... LARGE WALK IN CLOSET IN THE MASTER BEDROOM.  UNIT HAS GREAT VIEWS, LOTS OF TREES,  COMPLEX HAS A VERY NICE POOL,   VERY CLOSE TO INNISBROOK, SPC,  VERY CENTRALLY LOCATED.  YOU WILL NOT BE DISAPPOINTED.
